abstract: Jonathan Bush, a nephew and cousin of presidents and the founder of Athenahealth, which provides digital services to medical offices, resigned under pressure by the hedge fund Elliott Management.
snippet: Jonathan Bush, a nephew and cousin of presidents and the founder of Athenahealth, which provides digital services to medical offices, resigned under pressure by the hedge fund Elliott Management.
lead_paragraph: A member of one of America’s best-known political families resigned on Wednesday from the health care technology company he started more than two decades ago, in a victory for one of the world’s most powerful hedge funds.

abstract: The measure is considered the strictest in the nation. Voters backed it despite an expensive advertising campaign funded by a major tobacco company.
snippet: The measure is considered the strictest in the nation. Voters backed it despite an expensive advertising campaign funded by a major tobacco company.
lead_paragraph: Despite a $12 million ad blizzard by a giant tobacco company, voters in San Francisco resoundingly supported a new ban on the selling of flavored tobacco products, including vaping liquids packaged as candies and juice boxes, and menthol cigarettes.

abstract: The candidates, who edged out the former Los Angeles mayor Antonio Villaraigosa, are likely to battle over President Trump this fall. Democrats were in tight races in several Republican-held House districts.
snippet: The candidates, who edged out the former Los Angeles mayor Antonio Villaraigosa, are likely to battle over President Trump this fall. Democrats were in tight races in several Republican-held House districts.
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — Gavin Newsom, the Democratic lieutenant governor and former mayor of San Francisco, took a major step Tuesday in his bid to become California’s next governor, capturing one of two spots on the November ballot as the state moved closer to the end of the era of Gov. Jerry Brown.

abstract: Several prominent chief executives are considering running for president. But “the history of business leaders in the White House has not been good.”

lead_paragraph: Since Donald Trump was unexpectedly elected president on Nov. 8, 2016, speculation has swirled about whether another well-known business leader might make a bid for the White House in 2020.

abstract: A new plan would overhaul much of the system in just a decade — if elected leaders can summon the will to make it happen.
snippet: A new plan would overhaul much of the system in just a decade — if elected leaders can summon the will to make it happen.
lead_paragraph: The Metropolitan Transportation Authority has long estimated that it could take half a century to make New York City’s neglected subway system reliable. What a relief, then, to hear that the man Gov. Andrew Cuomo hired to fix this festering mess recently announced a plan that clocks in at a mere 10 years. Yes, you read that right — the promise of a modern, fully functional subway within a decade.
